In python 3.*.*


a) 
    pip install pyaudio -> error
    sudo apt-get install portaudio19-dev -> success
    pip install pyaudio -> success




b) how to install requirements.txt i.e. created from virtual environment of project via pip freeze > requirements.txt
   
   
    cd to the directory where requirements.txt is located.
    activate your virtualenv.
    run: pip install -r requirements.txt in your shell.
    
    
    
    
    
